DROP TABLE [dbo].[pecan_submit]

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[pecan_submit]
( 
	[ENTITY_ID] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[MARKER] [bigint] NULL,
	[QUERY_TYPE] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[PARTITIONS_SCANNED] [bigint]  NULL,
	[BYTES_SPILLED_TO_LOCAL_STORAGE] [bigint]  NULL,
	[BYTES_SPILLED_TO_REMOTE_STORAGE] [bigint]  NULL,
	[BYTES_SCANNED] [bigint]  NULL,
	[CREDITS_USED_CLOUD_SERVICES] [float]  NULL,
	[EXECUTION_TIME] [bigint]  NULL,
	[TOTAL_ELAPSED_TIME] [bigint]  NULL,
	[PERCENTAGE_SCANNED_FROM_CACHE] [float]  NULL,
	[BYTES_WRITTEN] [bigint]  NULL,
	[TRANSACTION_BLOCKED_TIME] [bigint]  NULL,
	[DATABASE_NAME] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[SCHEMA_NAME] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[WAREHOUSE_NAME] [nvarchar](max)  NULL
)
WITH
(
	DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
	HEAP
)
GO
